%}

### Protected endpoint (USER role required)
GET {{url}}/protected/user_demo/
Accept: application/json
Authorization: Bearer {{jwt_token}}

### Protected endpoint (ADMIN role required)
GET {{url}}/protected/admin_demo/
Accept: application/json
Authorization: Bearer {{jwt_token}}

